		"actions": {},
		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You have learned to combine magical and non-magical trickery together into a potent concoction of mischief. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Your Dexterity or Charisma score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You gain proficiency with the Deception skill or an expertise die if you are already proficient.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Half your bard levels count as rogue levels for the purpose of calculating your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.4727pnvz5nwn3h23]{Sneak Attack} damage.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">Half your rogue levels count as bard levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.6vy9t8q4cq53nw8v]{Bardic Legend} feature.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You gain proficiency with the Forgery kit and with a rare weapon with the finesse property of your choice.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
